rules.name: Rules Text
rules.text:
{color#ffffff}{fontsize-10}{1}{B}, Sacrifice another creature: Target creature gets -2/-2 until end of turn. Each player loses 1 life. You draw a card. Activate only as a sorcery.
You may cast this card from your graveyard transformed for {5}{B}{B}. If you do, it enters with a finality counter on it.{/fontsize-10}{/color#ffffff}
